# For Windows installation
python -m venv venv

### For Windows activation of virt env
.\venv\Scripts\activate

# download  Flask for the web server, Flask-CORS
pip install Flask Flask-CORS opencv-python Pillow numpy

# new version of image validation 
pip install python-dotenv 





Run this inside your venv:
pip install psycopg2-binary
If you want the source package instead:
pip install psycopg2
(But on Windows, psycopg2-binary is usually safer.)
Verify installation
After installation, run:
pip show psycopg2-binary
or
pip list
and check if it appears.

